---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/Section.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How We Know The Why collects, uses, and protects your information."
>
  <Section band="deep" class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto prose-invert">
      <h1 class="mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-secondary-text text-sm mb-8">Last updated: May 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-secondary-text leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-primary-text mb-3">Who we are</h2>
          <p>We Know The Why (WKTW) is a systems-driven growth agency. This policy describes how we handle information collected through weknowthewhy.com.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-primary-text mb-3">What we collect</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li><strong class="text-primary-text">Contact form submissions:</strong> Name, email, company, website URL, and message content.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-primary-text">Scan requests:</strong> Website URL, email, and company name.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-primary-text">Analytics:</strong> We use Plausible Analytics, which collects no personal data and uses no cookies, and runs at all times. We also use Google Analytics 4, delivered through Google Tag Manager, which sets cookies and collects usage data. Google Analytics is disabled by default and runs only after you accept it on our cookie banner (we use Google Consent Mode, so no analytics or advertising cookies are set until you opt in).</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-primary-text mb-3">How we use it</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>To respond to your inquiries</li>
            <li>To process and deliver scan results</li>
            <li>To improve our services and website</li>
            <li>We do not sell your information to third parties</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-primary-text mb-3">Cookies and consent</h2>
          <p>Plausible Analytics is cookieless and runs without consent. Google Analytics, loaded via Google Tag Manager, sets cookies and is switched off until you choose <strong class="text-primary-text">Accept</strong> on our cookie banner. Until then, Google Consent Mode keeps all analytics and advertising cookies disabled. You can change or withdraw your consent at any time using the <strong class="text-primary-text">Cookie settings</strong> link in the footer, or by clearing this site's data in your browser.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-primary-text mb-3">Data storage</h2>
          <p>Your data is stored securely using industry-standard practices. Contact and scan data is stored in Supabase (hosted on AWS). Payment processing is handled by Stripe — we never store payment card details.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-primary-text mb-3">Your rights</h2>
          <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data at any time by contacting us.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-primary-text mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p>Questions about this policy? <a href="/contact/">Contact us</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
